sentences: She is best known for her contributing vocals, banjo, and ukulele as a member of the Chapel Hill jazz band Squirrel Nut Zippers, a group that she founded in 1993 with then-husband Jimbo Mathus.
She took part in revival Zippers revival tours during the years 2007–09.
